description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and dynamic Advanced Nurse Practitioners to join the new innovative specialist multidisciplinary, Front of House Frailty Team at Darlington Memorial Hospital. We are in the process of developing a new team and pathways which involves the identification and management of frailty patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ANP will use expert knowledge and advanced clinical reasoning skills to provide specialist support and a comprehensive geriatric assessment to aid decision making and plans for ongoing management. The ANP will support admission avoidance and the Frailty Assessment Unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be part of a larger multi-disciplinary team including Consultant Geriatricians, ANPs and Therapists. This post would suit an experienced nurse who has an understanding of the management of people living with frailty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To discuss further please contact Matron Victoria Pye 07901117202&lt;/p&gt;
